<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-white">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 md:flex-row flex-col items-center">
        <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-1/2 lg:pr-24 md:pr-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left mb-16 md:mb-0 items-center text-center">
          <h1 class="title-font sm:text-5xl text-4xl mb-4 font-bold text-gray-900">Building Resilience, Fostering Peace</h1>
          <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed text-lg">Peace and Humanitarian Initiatives (PHI) is a non-governmental organisation committed to promoting sustainable peace, protecting human rights, and delivering humanitarian aid to vulnerable populations.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <a href="#projects" class="inline-flex text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-3 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg font-medium">See Our Projects</a>
            <a href="/about" class="ml-4 inline-flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 border-0 py-3 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-200 rounded text-lg font-medium">About PHI</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-1/2 w-5/6">
          <img class="object-contain w-full h-auto max-h-96" alt="Peace Dove - Symbol of Hope and Harmony" src="/public/peace-dove-hero.png" style="background: transparent;">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why We Exist Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-12">
          <h1 class="sm:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">The Challenges We Address</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-lg">In regions across Zimbabwe affected by conflict, poverty, and displacement, communities face systemic challenges. These include food insecurity, gender inequality, limited access to basic services, and the growing impact of climate-related disasters. PHI was founded to address these injustices and empower communities to build a more sustainable future.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">WHAT WE DO</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Core Objectives</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base">Our comprehensive, multi-faceted approach addresses the complex challenges faced by vulnerable communities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4 text-center">
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 w-full">
            <div class="h-full bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mb-4 mx-auto text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-bold title-font mb-3">Humanitarian Relief</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Providing critical emergency assistance—food, shelter, and medical care—to communities impacted by natural disasters, displacement, or war.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 w-full">
            <div class="h-full bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mb-4 mx-auto text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-bold title-font mb-3">Conflict Resolution & Peacebuilding</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Facilitating dialogue, mediation, and reconciliation to reduce violence and build sustainable peace in conflict-affected communities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 w-full">
            <div class="h-full bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mb-4 mx-auto text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-bold title-font mb-3">Community Empowerment</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Supporting local development through education, vocational training, and capacity-building programs that create resilient, self-reliant communities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/4 w-full">
            <div class="h-full bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 mb-4 mx-auto text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"></path>
              </svg>
              <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-bold title-font mb-3">Climate Resilience</h2>
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">Implementing integrated programs to mitigate the effects of floods and droughts through early warning systems, WASH infrastructure, and climate-smart agriculture.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Work in Action Section -->
    <section id="projects" class="text-gray-600 body-font bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-xs text-blue-500 tracking-widest font-medium title-font mb-1">OUR IMPACT</h2>
          <h1 class="sm:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Work in Action: The Tsholotsho Resilience Program</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap -m-4 items-center">
          <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full p-4">
            <div class="h-full">
              <img class="rounded-lg w-full object-cover object-center mb-6" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578469550956-0e16b69c6a3d?w=800" alt="Tsholotsho District Community">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center italic">Communities in Tsholotsho District working together for resilience</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full p-4">
            <div class="h-full">
              <p class="leading-relaxed text-lg mb-6">Tsholotsho District faces recurrent flooding and prolonged droughts, severely impacting livelihoods, infrastructure, and food security. PHI's Integrated Flood and Drought Resilience Program is on the ground, establishing local disaster committees, strengthening early warning systems, and promoting climate-smart agriculture to reduce vulnerability and build a safer future for the community.</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap mb-4">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mb-4">
                  <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">Local disaster committees established</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mb-4">
                  <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">Early warning systems strengthened</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mb-4">
                  <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">Climate-smart agriculture promoted</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mb-4">
                  <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-gray-700">WASH infrastructure improved</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <a href="/mission" class="inline-flex text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-3 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg font-medium">Explore the Tsholotsho Project</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stay Connected Newsletter Section -->
    <section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
      <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-12">
          <h1 class="sm:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold title-font mb-4 text-gray-900">Stay Connected to Our Mission</h1>
          <p class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto leading-relaxed text-lg">Get updates from the field and learn how we are making a difference in communities across Zimbabwe. Join our mailing list.</p>
        </div>
        <form class="flex lg:w-2/3 w-full sm:flex-row flex-col mx-auto px-8 sm:space-x-4 sm:space-y-0 space-y-4 sm:px-0 items-end">
          <div class="relative flex-grow w-full">
            <label for="email" class="leading-7 text-sm text-gray-600">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" required class="w-full bg-white rounded border border-gray-300 focus:border-blue-500 focus:bg-transparent focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-200 text-base outline-none text-gray-700 py-3 px-4 leading-8 transition-colors duration-200 ease-in-out">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="text-white bg-blue-500 border-0 py-3 px-8 focus:outline-none hover:bg-blue-600 rounded text-lg font-medium">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>